subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: This project aims to provide technical and advisory support to the Ministry of Municipal and Rural Affairs (MOMRA) to produce a comprehensive strategy for rural development through conducting extensive researches and studies of the elements and determinants of development and the development of institutional capacity and human resources.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Rural Development Strategy
